;white-space:nowrap;left:0.71mm;top:2.99mm;height:3.18mm;width:76.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs12">0x01 = 복사방지 설정</span></div><div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0.71mm;top:6.17mm;height:3.18mm;width:76.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs12">0x02 = 인쇄방지 설정</span></div><div class="hls ps2" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0.71mm;top:-0.18mm;height:3.18mm;width:28.43mm;"><span class="hrt cs12">전체 길이</span></div><div class="hls ps2" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0.71mm;top:-0.18mm;height:3.18mm;width:18.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs12">82</span></div></div></div></div><div class="hpN" style="left:180mm;top:282mm;width:2.12mm;height:4.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">6</span></div></div><div class="hpa" style="width:210mm;height:297mm;"><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:20mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps45"><span class="htC" style="width:12.35mm;height:100%;"></span><span class="hrt cs4">ᄒᆞᆫ글 문서</span><span class="hrt cs39">&nbsp;파일 형식 – 배포용 문서</span></div></div></div><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:35mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps44" style="line-height:4.59mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:0.00mm;height:4.59mm;width:130.60mm;"><div class="hhe" style="display:inline-block;margin-left:0mm;width:4.90mm;height:3.53mm;"><span class="hrt cs1" style="font-size:10pt;">2.</span></div><span class="hrt cs38">배포용 문서 데이터 복호화</span></div></div></div><div class="hpN" style="left:180mm;top:282mm;width:2.12mm;height:4.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">7</span></div></div><div class="hpa" style="width:210mm;height:297mm;"><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:20mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps45"><span class="htC" style="width:12.35mm;height:100%;"></span><span class="hrt cs4">ᄒᆞᆫ글 문서</span><span class="hrt cs39">&nbsp;파일 형식 – 배포용 문서</span></div></div></div><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:35mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:0.00mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">다음은 “배포용 문서 데이터”를 통해 스트림을 복호화하는 과정을 설명한다.</span></div></div></div><div class="hpN" style="left:180mm;top:282mm;width:2.12mm;height:4.23mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">8</span></div></div><div class="hpa" style="width:210mm;height:297mm;"><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:20mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps45"><span class="htC" style="width:12.35mm;height:100%;"></span><span class="hrt cs4">ᄒᆞᆫ글 문서</span><span class="hrt cs39">&nbsp;파일 형식 – 배포용 문서</span></div></div></div><div class="hcD" style="left:30mm;top:35mm;"><div class="hcI"><div class="hls ps39" style="line-height:92.71mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:0.00mm;height:92.71mm;width:130.60mm;"><div class="hsR" style="top:0mm;left:0mm;margin-bottom:0mm;margin-right:0mm;width:40.85mm;height:92.71mm;display:inline-block;position:relative;vertical-align:middle;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url('images/distribution/BIN0002.bmp');"></div></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:96.41mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"></div><div class="hls ps19" style="line-height:4.06mm;white-space:nowrap;left:6.00mm;top:106.47mm;height:4.06mm;width:144.00mm;"><div class="hhe" style="display:inline-block;margin-left:0mm;width:9.80mm;height:3.53mm;"><span class="hrt cs1" style="font-size:10pt;">1.1.</span></div><span class="hrt cs14">Seed 찾기</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:114.72mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">복호화과정에 필요한 Seed값은 &nbsp;“배포용 문서 데이터”의 처음 4바이트이다.</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:121.94mm;height:3.53mm;width:0.00mm;"></div><div class="hls ps19" style="line-height:4.06mm;white-space:nowrap;left:6.00mm;top:150.22mm;height:4.06mm;width:144.00mm;"><div class="hhe" style="display:inline-block;margin-left:0mm;width:9.80mm;height:3.53mm;"><span class="hrt cs1" style="font-size:10pt;">2.2.</span></div><span class="hrt cs14">난수 배열 만들기</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:158.47mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">배포용 문서 데이터에서 해시코드를 추출하기 위해서는 우선 특정패턴을 지닌 난수배</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:164.11mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">열을 생성해야 한다. 이때 패턴을 생성하기 위해 MS Visual C의 랜덤함수(srand(),&nbsp;</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:169.76mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">rand())를 사용한다.</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:177.17mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">srand()의 초기 값은 앞서 찾은 Seed를 입력하며, rand()함수의 결과값에 따라 배열의&nbsp;</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:182.81mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">값이 채워진다.</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:3.53mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:190.22mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"><span class="hrt cs0">배열의 값이 채워지는 방식은 다음과 같다.</span></div><div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:2.79mm;white-space:nowrap;left:12.35mm;top:197.45mm;height:3.53mm;width:130.60mm;"></div></div></div><div class="htG" style="left:42.35mm;width:133.12mm;top:194.16mm;height:28.69mm;"><div class="htb" style="left:1mm;width:130.12mm;top:7mm;height:14.52mm;"><svg class="hs" viewBox="-2.5 -2.5 135.12 19.52" style="left:-2.5mm;top:-2.5mm;width:135.12mm;height:19.52mm;"><defs></defs><path fill="url(#w_00)" d="M0,0L30.84,0L30.84,5.17L0,5.17L0,0Z "></path><path fill="url(#w_00)" d="M30.84,0L51.48,0L51.48,5.17L30.84,5.17L30.84,0Z "></path><path fill="url(#w_00)" d="M51.48,0L130.13,0L130.13,5.17L51.48,5.17L51.48,0Z "></path><path fill="url(#w_00)" d="M0,9.35L30.84,9.35L30.84,14.52L0,14.52L0,9.35Z "></